                                    "abstract": "The Chinese People's Association for Friendship with Foreign Countries held a reception in Beijing on November 29 to celebrate the 75th anniversary of the establishment of diplomatic relations between China and seven Central and Eastern European countries. The event was attended by Tie Ning, Vice Chairman of the Standing Committee of the National People's Congress. Ambassadors and representatives from Bulgaria, Romania, the Czech Republic, Slovakia, Hungary, Poland, and Albania, as well as representatives from various sectors, were among the approximately 200 attendees.",
                                    "content": "中新网 北京11月30日电 (记者 余湛奕)中国人民对外友好协会29日在北京举办庆祝中国同中东欧七国建交75周年招待会,全国人大常委会副委员长铁凝出席。保加利亚、罗马尼亚、捷克、斯洛伐克、匈牙利、波兰、阿尔巴尼亚驻华使节及各界代表约200人参加。(完)",
