                                    "title": "Pakistan provides China with fresh information on TTP activities in Afghanistan",
                                    "url": "https://www.khaama.com/pakistan-provides-china-with-fresh-information-on-ttp-activities-in-afghanistan/",
                                    "date": "2024-11-19 17:11:37",
