                                    "data_source": "zjw",
                                    "abstract": "During a recent visit to Brazil, Chinese President Xi Jinping and Brazilian President Luiz Inácio Lula da Silva held talks and jointly signed and issued a joint statement, indicating the direction for future deepening of defense cooperation between the two countries. This year marks the 50th anniversary of the establishment of diplomatic relations between China and Brazil. In recent years, the two militaries have strengthened exchanges and dialogue at all levels, deepening mutual understanding. China has always viewed and developed military relations with Brazil from a strategic perspective. China is willing to work together with Brazil to further strengthen military cooperation under the strategic guidance of the two heads of state, enhance the ability to jointly address challenges, and make positive contributions to building a China-Brazil community of shared destiny for a more just world and a more sustainable planet.",
                                    "content": "11月28日下午，国防部举行例行记者会，国防部新闻局局长、国防部新闻发言人吴谦大校答记者问。记者：习近平主席近日访问巴西期间，中巴发表联合声明称，两国在国防和国防工业领域拥有合作潜力，应加强高层交往并探讨新合作设想。请进一步介绍中巴两军关系情况。吴谦：11月中下旬，习近平主席应邀出席二十国集团领导人第十九次峰会并对巴西进行国事访问。期间，习主席同巴西总统卢拉举行会谈，共同签署并发表联合声明，就双方未来深化防务领域合作指明了方向。今年是中巴建交50周年。近年来，中巴两军加强各级别交往对话，相互了解不断加深。中方始终从战略高度看待和发展两军关系。我们愿与巴方共同努力，在两国元首战略引领下，进一步加强两军合作，提升共同应对挑战能力，为构建更公正世界和更可持续星球的中巴命运共同体作出积极贡献。",
