                                    "title": "Putin says Russia hopes to build strong relations with Afghanistan",
                                    "url": "https://www.ariananews.af/putin-says-russia-hopes-to-build-strong-relations-with-afghanistan/",
                                    "date": "2024-11-29 05:10:24",
