                                    "data_source": "zjw",
                                    "abstract": "Israeli Prime Minister Benjamin Netanyahu held talks with US envoy Amos Hochstein at the Prime Minister's office regarding the ceasefire between Israel and Lebanon. Hochstein visited Lebanon earlier in the week to promote a ceasefire agreement between Israel and Hezbollah. Additionally, Hochstein is scheduled to meet with Israel's new Defense Minister Benny Gantz on the same day. On November 20, Hochstein met again with Lebanese National Assembly Speaker Nabih Berri in Beirut. Hochstein stated that he would not publicly discuss the results of the negotiations or the points of discussion, but he could say that progress has been made and that he will work with the new US administration on all issues.",
                                    "content": "【环球网报道】据《以色列时报》21日最新消息，以色列总理内塔尼亚胡与美国总统特使阿莫斯·霍克斯坦在以总理办公室就黎以停火问题举行会谈。报道称，霍克斯坦本周早些时候访问黎巴嫩，旨在推动以色列与黎巴嫩真主党之间达成停火协议。此外，报道提到，霍克斯坦还计划于当地时间21日16时与以色列新任国防部长卡茨会面。当地时间11月20日，霍克斯坦在黎巴嫩首都贝鲁特与黎巴嫩国民议会议长纳比·贝里再次举行会晤。霍克斯坦表示，将不会公开谈论谈判结果或讨论的要点，但可以说已经取得了进展，并将与美国新政府就所有问题展开合作。",
