                                    "title": "伊党土团党内部矛盾加剧 法米:两党随时崩裂",
                                    "url": "https://www.enanyang.my/%E8%A6%81%E9%97%BB/%E4%BC%8A%E5%85%9A%E5%9C%9F%E5%9B%A2%E5%85%9A%E5%86%85%E9%83%A8%E7%9F%9B%E7%9B%BE%E5%8A%A0%E5%89%A7-%E6%B3%95%E7%B1%B3%E4%B8%A4%E5%85%9A%E9%9A%8F%E6%97%B6%E5%B4%A9%E8%A3%82",
                                    "date": "2024-11-26 16:00:00",
                                    "news_id": "67460d4e9e140ab22b71338e",
                                    "data_source": "zjw",
                                    "abstract": "The relationship between the Islamic Party (PAS) and the United Indigenous Party (Bersatu) within the Perikatan Nasional (PN) coalition is described as precarious and on the verge of collapse by People's Justice Party (PKR) publicity chief, Fahmi Fadzil. He points out that internal issues within PN, such as the controversy over the \"poster boy\" or prime ministerial candidate, and the recent replacement of two Bersatu state assemblymen in Perlis, have exacerbated tensions between the two parties. Fahmi, who is also the Minister of Communications, further criticizes the opposition's performance in the lower house of parliament, stating that they have failed to address substantive issues and have not been able to propose an alternative budget for two consecutive years. He also comments on the controversy surrounding the use of bilingual signs, stating that local authorities have established regulations for the languages used in shops and premises, and that this should not be a point of contention. He emphasizes that if a sign has been in violation of these regulations, action should not be taken years later, as this could create an impression of unfair enforcement.",
                                    "content": "(吉隆坡26日讯)人民公正党宣传主任法米指出,目前国盟面临数个内部课题,反映出伊斯兰党与土著团结党之间的关系岌岌可危,并形容犹如“裂缝”随时会崩裂。 他说,从国盟的“海报男孩”即首相人选争议,直至玻璃市土团党州议员被撤换,使到两党的关系更趋僵持不下。 他说,除了内部问题,反对党的制衡表现显得苍白,特别是在国会下议院。 “最近我们看到国盟主席被要求寻找新的海报男孩(首相人选),玻州2土团党州议员被撤换,还有登嘉楼大型活动没邀请土团党最高领导层,这些都是国盟内部矛盾的显现,关系越来越紧张。 “此外,反对党在国会的表现也糟糕,他们无法讨论实质性课题,甚至连续两年无法提出替代预算案。我们看到这随时会崩裂的裂痕。” 法米也是通讯部长,他今日出席MYTV Mana-Mana应用程式推介礼后,向记者这么说。 根据本地新闻网站报道,玻州土团党2名州议员被撤换并非职责表现,而是基于政治因数。 此外,针对招牌使用双语的争议,法米说,地方政府已制定商店或场所使用语言的规定,因此,此事不应该成为争议,业者必须遵守规定。 “如果招牌早已违规,就不要等到数年后才采取行动,因为这会引起公众对执法不公平的印象。必须一开始就公平。”",
